+	// Reject paths at or under the daemon's workspaces root. The GC loop
+	// reclaims anything in that tree, so a local_directory pinned there would
+	// be swept once idle. Check both the literal cleaned path (what the GC
+	// enumerates) and the symlink-resolved realPath (where writes actually
